prediction.sparql:
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?stadium ?label WHERE {
  ?stadium wdt:P31 wd:Q1154710 .
  ?stadium wdt:P84 wd:Q1208016 .
  ?stadium rdfs:label ?label .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?label ) , "stadium" ) ) FILTER ( LANG( ?label ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?league ?leagueLabel WHERE {
  ?league wdt:P31 wd:Q623109 .
  ?league wdt:P4794 wd:Q118 .
  ?league rdfs:label ?leagueLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?leagueLabel ) = "en" ) FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?leagueLabel ) , "league" ) )
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?event ?date WHERE {
  wd:Q8018 p:P793 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P793 wd:Q125375 ; pq:P585 ?date .
  BIND( wd:Q125375 AS ?event )
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
SELECT ?follower ?followerLabel ?start WHERE {
  ?follower wdt:P39 wd:Q271148 .
  ?follower p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q271148 ; pq:P580 ?start .
  FILTER ( ?start > "0875-08-16" ^^ xsd:date ) FILTER ( ?follower != wd:Q215204 ) OPTIONAL {
    ?follower rdfs:label ?followerLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?followerLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
ORDER BY ?start

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?sacrament WHERE {
  wd:Q3233636 wdt:P527 ?sacrament .
  ?sacrament rdfs:label ?label .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?label ) , "marriage" ) ) FILTER ( LANG( ?label ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?award WHERE {
  wd:Q1964769 p:P166 ?awardStatement .
  ?awardStatement ps:P166 ?award .
  ?awardStatement pq:P585 ?date .
  FILTER ( YEAR( ?date ) = 1947 )
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
SELECT ?position ?positionLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q590227 p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 ?position .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?startTime .
  FILTER ( ?startTime = "1936-01-20T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime ) OPTIONAL {
    ?position rdfs:label ?positionLabel FILTER ( lang( ?positionLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
SELECT ?actor ?actorLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q147235 p:P161 ?castStatement .
  ?castStatement ps:P161 ?actor .
  ?castStatement pq:P453 ?character .
  ?character rdfs:label ?characterLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?characterLabel ) = "en" ) FILTER ( ?characterLabel = "Naomi" ) OPTIONAL {
    ?actor rdfs:label ?actorLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?actorLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?song ?label WHERE {
  ?song wdt:P31 wd:Q7366 .
  ?song rdfs:label ?label .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?label ) , "world" ) ) FILTER ( LANG( ?label ) = "en" )
}
LIMIT 20
